      "span_text": "To amplify all eight segments in a single reaction, RT-PCR was conducted on RNA templates using Uni-12, Uni-13, and polymerase gene primers as previously described [CITATION_1] plus Invitrogen SuperScript III One-Step Reverse Transcriptase and Platinum Taq HiFi (Invitrogen)."
    }
